Playing around with Condition from @JohnSanGiovanni 
What's the best #? What's the worst? Is it poss to get 5 pts? Posbl to get 0? Why?
Pick a # btwn 0 & 100. 
Get a pt if your #...
Is odd
Has an even # in tens place
Is composite
Is a multiple of 10
Is not a multiple of 5
